    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1223868743667552256",
    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年4月3日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年4月9日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年4月10日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：新增<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #f8f8f9; float: none; display: inline;\">非授权第三方软件发品的违规场景和处理措施。</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">原规则链接：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12</a></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">修订部分如下：</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 431.5pt; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"575\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 215.75pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"288\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 215.75pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"288\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 319.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 215.75pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 319.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"288\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">①19.1.8商品发布渠道不合规：虚拟商品发布渠道不合规指未按照《京东行业运营标准》规定的通过虚拟商品发布渠道进行发布商品的违规行为。虚拟商品发布操作路径详见：http://psm.jd.com/article/articledetail.html?id=671<br />②19.2.8商品发布渠道不合规<br />19.2.8.1违规程度轻微：警告，违规商品搜索、推荐降权（降权比例基于严重程度25%-100%不等）；<br />19.2.8.2违规程度一般：警告，违规商品屏蔽；<br />19.2.8.3违规程度严重：警告，违规商品下架；<br />19.2.8.4违规程度极其严重：警告，违规商品删除。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 215.75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 319.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"288\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">①19.1.8 商品发布渠道不合规：<br />19.1.8.1虚拟商品发布渠道不合规：指未按照《京东行业运营标准》规定的通过虚拟商品发布渠道进行发布商品的违规行为。 虚拟商品发布操作路径详见： http://psm.jd.com/article/articledetail.html?id=671<br />19.1.8.2非授权第三方软件发品：指通过使用非京东官方软件工具，也非服务商在京麦服务市场中提供的软件工具进行发品的违规行为，管理公告详见：https://mtt.jd.com/article/articleView/b6bc1d74-a2b3-48b5-97ad-2d77c183f55b<br />②19.2.8 商品发布渠道不合规<br />19.2.8.1违规程度轻微：警告，违规商品搜索、推荐降权、限制在售商品阈值；<br />19.2.8.2违规程度一般：限制创建商品、限制通过接口批量操作商品、违规商品屏蔽；<br />19.2.8.3违规程度严重：禁止上架待售商品、违规商品下架；<br />19.2.8.4违规程度极其严重：禁止发品、违规商品删除；</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
